casebody.data:
Thomas W. CUTLER and Ann Cutler, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
U.S. BANK NATIONAL ASSOCIATION, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D16-4086 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 23, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellants' motion for rehearing en bane is stricken as insufficient, in that it fails to identify an issue of great public importance or explain how en bane consideration of the case is necessary to maintain consistency with this court's decisions. Appellants' motion for rehearing, for written opinion, or for certification is denied.
